trans-unit.source: Specifies the icon to display in **Solution Explorer** for a custom project item type.
trans-unit.target: 指定针对自定义项目项类型要在解决方案资源管理器中显示的图标。

trans-unit.source: Apply this attribute to an implementation of the <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItemTypeProvider> interface to specify the icon to display for the project item type.
trans-unit.target: 将此特性应用于的实现<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItemTypeProvider>接口来指定要显示的项目项类型的图标。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [How to: Define a SharePoint Project Item Type](/visualstudio/sharepoint/how-to-define-a-sharepoint-project-item-type.md).
trans-unit.target: 有关详细信息，请参阅[如何： 定义 SharePoint 项目项类型](/visualstudio/sharepoint/how-to-define-a-sharepoint-project-item-type.md)。

trans-unit.source: Use an embedded 24-bit .bmp or .ico resource for the icon, with magenta (255,0,255) as the transparent color.
trans-unit.target: 使用带有洋红色 (255，0255) 作为透明颜色的图标嵌入的 24 位.bmp 或.ico 资源。

trans-unit.source: The recommended size for icons is 16 pixels wide by 16 pixels high.
trans-unit.target: 图标的建议的大小是 16 像素宽 x 16 像素高。

trans-unit.source: The namespace qualified name of an embedded .bmp or .ico resource to use as the icon for a custom project item type.
trans-unit.target: 要用作自定义项目项类型图标的嵌入式 .bmp 或 .ico 资源的命名空间限定的名称。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.SharePointProjectItemIconAttribute" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.SharePointProjectItemIconAttribute" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: Use 24-bit images for the icon, with magenta (255,0,255) as the transparent color.
trans-unit.target: 使用带有洋红色 (255，0255) 作为透明颜色的图标 24 位映像。

trans-unit.source: The recommended size for icons is 16 pixels wide by 16 pixels high.
trans-unit.target: 图标的建议的大小是 16 像素宽 x 16 像素高。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the namespace qualified name of an embedded .bmp or .ico resource to use as the icon for a custom project item type.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置要用作自定义项目项类型图标的嵌入式 .bmp 或 .ico 资源的命名空间限定的名称。

trans-unit.source: The namespace qualified name of an embedded .bmp or .ico resource to use as the icon for a custom project item type.
trans-unit.target: 嵌入.bmp 或.ico 资源使用图标作为一个自定义项目项类型的命名空间限定的名称。
